    "The average response (at the note level) by the included reviews for the four yes/no questions are included in Table 2.",
    "Overall reviewers considered ChatGPT's response to be 96.5% and 98% correct for MMSE and CDR respectively.",
    "The assessment for whether ChatGPT's answers are also complete (i.e.",
    "they do not miss anything) was slightly lower averaging about 84% and 83% for MMSE and CDR respectively.",
    "The inter-rater-agreements between reviewers were calculated based on Fleiss' Kappa and are summarized in Table 3."
  ],
